@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "FAQs";
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>@ViewData["Title"]</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-image: url('/images/digital-art-8015896_1280.jpeg');
            background-size: cover;
            background-attachment: fixed;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #FAEBD7;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .divider {
            border-top: 1px solid #fff; 
            margin-top: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .ole_text {
            font-family: creepster;
            color: darkred;
            font-size: large;
        }

        .faq-section {
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

            .faq-section h2 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }

        .faq-question {
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #8b0000; 
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

            .btn:hover {
                background-color: #4b0000; 
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>FAQs</h1>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <div class="faq-section">
            <h2>Common Questions</h2>
            <div class="faq-question">
                <h3>1. How can I survive against the undead?</h3>
                <p>Answer: You can survive by scavenging for resources, building alliances with other survivors, and fortifying your shelter against zombie attacks.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-question">
                <h3>2. Are there different types of zombies in the game?</h3>
                <p>Answer: Yes, there are different types of zombies with varying strengths and weaknesses. Some are faster, while others are stronger and more resilient.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-question">
                <h3>3. Can I customize my character?</h3>
                <p>Answer: Absolutely! You can customize your character's appearance, skills, and gear to adapt to different challenges in the post-apocalyptic world.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-question">
                <h3>4. Is there a crafting system in the game?</h3>
                <p>Answer: Yes, there is a robust crafting system that allows you to create weapons, tools, and fortifications using materials found in the game world.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-question">
                <h3>5. How can I defend my shelter from zombie hordes?</h3>
                <p>Answer: You can set up traps, barricades, and recruit other survivors to help defend your shelter against zombie hordes.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <a href="/" class="btn">Back to Home</a>
    </div>
    <!-- Include any necessary scripts here -->
</body>
</html>